title: Extreme Limits aka Crash Point Zero
description: R | 1h 33min | Action, Adventure, Drama | March 23rd 2001 A scientist recovers a powerful weapon created by inventor Nicola Tesla in the early twentieth century. Now, the plane carrying the device and a disparate group of passengers crashes in the Canadian mountains. The battle to survive begins.
